The new template has removed the `Startup.cs` and you are resgistering the services inside the main method - I think this needs to change:
* Seporation of concern is very important for maintainability.
* The Blazor template needs to be consistaint with othe ASP projects, which all use `Startup.css`.

The tricky thing is that `HttpClient` need a referece to the builder.  
